05_Cognitive

Subjective Graph Literacy

SGL scores ranged from 10 to 58 with an average score of 36 (red dotted line).

There was no significant relationship between age and graph literacy, r = -0.108, p = 0.119

Numeracy

Numeracy scores ranged from 0 to 14 with an average score of 9 (red dotted line).

There was a significant increase in numeracy with age, r = 0.23, p = 0.001.
